# DevPulse API

A collaborative platform for software teams to report bugs, suggest features, and manage issue resolutions.

---

# Live URL

```bash
https://your-live-url.com
```

---

# Project Overview

DevPulse is a RESTful API built with Node.js, Express.js, TypeScript, and PostgreSQL.  
It allows contributors and maintainers to manage software issues efficiently with secure JWT authentication and role-based authorization.

---

# Features

- User Registration & Login
- JWT Authentication
- Role-Based Authorization
- Password Hashing with bcrypt
- Create Issues
- Get All Issues
- Get Single Issue
- Update Issues
- Delete Issues
- PostgreSQL Integration
- Raw SQL Queries using `pg`
- Centralized Error Handling
- Modular Architecture
- Environment Variable Configuration

